## 🛠️ Project Structure

```text
optimization_core/
├── configs/               # YAML Configurations
├── docs/                  # 📚 Comprehensive Documentation
├── factories/             # Component Registries (Optimizers, etc.)
├── trainers/              # Core Training Logic
├── scripts/               # Utility Scripts
└── train_llm.py           # Main Entry Point
```

